narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it! It's a great way to improve your writing skills.
A fantastic exploration and training in writing narrative essays. A good introduction into whatever future writing you may want to pursue. TAKE IT.
If you like reading and writing non-fiction essays and if you are willing to put in the effort to write an essay every weak, simply put, this class is for you.

I loved this class! Each day was a thorough discussion of a selection of modern essays. Voice and style were both focused on heavily, and I certainly grew as a writer throughout the semester. If you're just looking to improve your writing, this is a wonderful class to take--you'll get helpful feedback from both your instructor and classmates.
I would very much recommend this class.
